Package projeto_pp

Class EditionImpl

java.lang.Object
projeto_pp.EditionImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, ma02_resources.project.Edition
public class EditionImpl extends Object implements ma02_resources.project.Edition, Serializable
The EditionImpl class represents an implementation of the Edition interface and provides functionality to manage a CBL edition. This class implements the Serializable interface, allowing instances of EditionImpl to be serialized and deserialized.

    • addProject

      public void addProject(String name, String description, String[] tags) throws IOException, ParseException
      Adds a new project to the edition.The method checks if projects is full, if it is this method calls extendsProject. It also checks if the name, description or tags are null. Then it assigns a project created by reading the template to temp, the values of name, string, tags and maximumNumberOfTasks are given to temp. Following that the temp project is assigned to a new index in projects.
      Specified by:
      addProject in interface ma02_resources.project.Edition
      Parameters:
      name - The name of the project.
      description - The description of the project.
      tags - The contributors of the project.
      Throws:
      IOException - If readProject can't read the template.
      ParseException - If the readProject cannot be parsed.
